 1 indicates an outcome occurs less frequently than for individuals who are White.</div>\n<br/>\n</div>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n::: {.panel-tabset}\n\n### Sentence Length\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); justify-items: center;\">\n<div id=\"htmlwidget-7e08370de282c58d83ee\" style=\"width:100%;height:650px;\" class=\"highchart html-widget \"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-7e08370de282c58d83ee\">{\"x\":{\"hc_opts\":{\"chart\":{\"reflow\":true,\"marginTop\":100,\"marginBottom\":80,\"spacingBottom\":80,\"width\":300,\"height\":300},\"title\":{\"text\":\"Black People, Non-Hispanic\"},\"yAxis\":{\"title\":\"\",\"type\":\"linear\",\"categories\":{\"0\":\" \",\"1\":\"1 = White<br>Reference Line\",\"2\":\" \",\"3\":\" \",\"4\":\" \",\"5\":\" \",\"6\":\" \",\"7\":\" \"},\"labels\":{\"rotation\":0,\"step\":1},\"min\":0,\"max\":7,\"plotBands\":[{\"color\":\"rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)\",\"from\":0,\"to\":1}]},\"credits\":{\"enabled\":false},\"exporting\":{\"enabled\":false},\"boost\":{\"enabled\":false},\"plotOptions\":{\"series\":{\"label\":{\"enabled\":false},\"turboThreshold\":0,\"showInLegend\":true,\"stacking\":\"normal\"},\"treemap\":{\"layoutAlgorithm\":\"squarified\"},\"scatter\":{\"marker\":{\"symbol\":\"circle\"}},\"bar\":{\"dataLabels\":{\"enabled\":true,\"format\":\"{point.rri}\",\"style\":{\"fontSize\":\"12px\"}}}},\"series\":[{\"name\":\"Overrepresented\",\"data\":[{\"race_eth\":\"Black, non-Hispanic\",\"sample\":\"In Prison\",\"rri\":6,\"state\":\"Delaware\",\"colorv\":\"#ff6400\",\"tooltip\":\"Black, non-Hispanic people are 6 times more likely <br>to be in prison than White people.\",\"type\":\"Overrepresented\",\"rri_label\":\"500% more likely\",\"y\":6,\"name\":\"In Prison\"},{\"race_eth\":\"Black, non-Hispanic\",\"sample\":\"Sentence Length < 1 year\",\"rri\":4,\"state\":\"Delaware\",\"colorv\":\"#ff6400\",\"tooltip\":\"Black, non-Hispanic people are 